issues.title: Upgrade Apache Commons Collections to v3.2.2
issues.body:
Version 3.2.1 has a CVSS 10.0 vulnerability. That's the worst kind of
vulnerability that exists. By merely existing on the classpath, this
library causes the Java serialization parser for the entire JVM process
to go from being a state machine to a turing machine. A turing machine
with an exec() function!

https://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2015-8103
https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-collections/security-reports.html
http://foxglovesecurity.com/2015/11/06/what-do-weblogic-websphere-jboss-jenkins-opennms-and-your-application-have-in-common-this-vulnerability/

commit.message: 更新队列以及删除一些pom配置

Merge remote-tracking branch 'origin/newVersion' into newVersion

# Conflicts:
#	Egg-main/src/main/java/edu/xiyou/andrew/Egg/example/demo.java
测试发现，会丢失一些网页，修复该功能
提交可以匹配正文的类
This is last version of Egg, but it just for my engineering course exercise, the code same as https://github.com/wangduoxiong/WebCrawler. How over it will well maintain by me for a long time.
提交从网页中匹配链接所需的类LinkList
增加任务存入取出队列接口Scheduler， 并实现QueueScheduler类
增加LinkFilter类，能够过滤出所需要的链接
添加一些以前的工具类
很蛋疼，本来打算自己写的，写着写着又变成模仿了，在后面的更新会慢慢修改回自己的东西。
增加StardardGererator 种子生成器，其余类部分修改
修改CrawlDatum的状态常量名称并增加一常量，增加SegmentWrite两个方法和增加注释
种子生成器Generator接口，能够返回下一个种子
增加BerkeleyDBFactory类，传入数据库环境和数据库名返回实例
增加SegmentWrite类,可以将爬取时的数据写入数据库，能将爬取数据持久化

增加链接的基础类Link类
增加过滤出链
接的LinkFilter类

增加HttpHeaderMetadata接口
增加HttpResponseHeaders类
HttpHeaders更名为HttpRequestHeaders类
